A minimalistic illustration of a scattered deck of playing cards spread across a sleek hotel room floor, each card showing simple line drawings of different exercise poses like lunges, stretches, and squats. A compact travel suitcase sits partially open nearby, with running shoes and a rolled yoga mat visible inside. The color palette is clean and muted—soft grays, whites, and one accent color of teal. The composition is shot from above, bird's eye view, creating a flat-lay aesthetic. The room suggests travel with a corner of a crisp white hotel bed visible at the edge of frame. Empty space dominates, emphasizing the portable, anywhere-fitness concept.
